data.description: What a wonderful opportunity to own this beautiful corner lot home! Turn key 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in a centrally located area close to schools, shopping center and restaurants.  This home features updated open kitchen with quartz counter top, gas stove, refrigerator and washer and dryer. House has natural light, and vaulted ceilings.  Also, this home has just been renovated with new tiles throughout,  new base board,  door frames and a new AC unit.  Ramp for a boat and van.  Low HOA and  there is additional parking for guess.
